[
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切如來大祕密王未曾有最上",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "微妙大曼拏羅經卷第一",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試鴻臚少卿明教大師臣天息災奉　詔譯1 相應行曼拏羅儀則品相應行曼拏羅儀則品第一如是我聞：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時，世尊在忉利天大善法堂。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時乃有無數最上天人及龍、夜叉、羅剎、乾闥婆、阿修羅、迦樓羅、緊曩羅、摩睺羅伽、必里多、大力、阿波娑摩囉、拏吉儞、部多、吠多拏、相應相母鬼等，是等厭於生死欲斷輪迴，圍遶世尊求吉祥法，亦復樂求無盡金剛界廣大智成就法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時復有無數為利三界作變化相清淨智大菩薩，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0541c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智金剛菩薩、智鉤菩薩、智欲菩薩、智密菩薩、灌頂吉祥菩薩、大威神吉祥菩薩、幢吉祥菩薩、念吉祥菩薩、法音菩薩、智慧猛菩薩、因猛菩薩、口猛菩薩、變化業菩薩、變化界菩薩、變化夜叉菩薩、變化祕密菩薩，如是等菩薩摩訶薩皆悉證得法智祕密三昧。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有四族母，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "圓智三昧金剛母、寶智三昧金剛母、法智三昧金剛母、羯磨智三昧金剛母。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有四大神通菩薩，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金剛婆叉神通菩薩、金剛妙入神通菩薩、金剛不動光神通菩薩、金剛喜神通菩薩。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有八大祕密化身顯供養菩薩，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金剛樂菩薩、金剛色菩薩、金剛妙音菩薩、金剛愛菩薩、金剛薩寫菩薩、金剛頗羅菩薩、金剛最上莊嚴菩薩、金剛妙香菩薩。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有十六大力自在藥叉大忿怒明王等，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "左無畏大忿怒明王、無能勝大忿怒明王、能成就大忿怒明王、最上蓮花明大忿怒明王、馬首大忿怒明王、蓮花軍茶利大忿怒明王、淨光大忿怒明王、甘露軍茶利大忿怒明王、大力大忿怒明王、普光大忿怒明王、呬嚕迦大忿怒明王、嚕左迦大忿怒明王、無邊大忿怒明王、金剛不動大忿怒明王、多囉大忿怒明王、祖那大忿怒明王、白繖蓋大忿怒明王、最上明大忿怒明王、六面大忿怒明王。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有十六大女形明王等，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "多羅大明王、無能勝大明王、孔雀大明王、金剛鉤大明王、大稱大明王、顰眉大明王、摩摩枳大明王、金剛鎖大明王、金剛拳大明王、白色大明王、寶髻大明王、金剛行步大明王、金剛身大明王、金剛香大明王、持世大明王。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有四相應相女形大明王，復有六十四大金剛拏吉爾。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有四大地天，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不動大地天、黃面大地天、黑白色大地天、紅面大地天。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等大地天能成就一切事，能施一切欲，能安住一切法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有八大瘧者，其名曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金剛口大瘧者、黃面大瘧者、醜面大瘧者、紅身大瘧者、多面大瘧者、三髻大瘧者、食血大瘧者、赤黃大瘧者。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等大瘧者，常侵害有情，令彼有情失於色力，或奪其命。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等天及彼天主、持明天持明天主，乃至龍及龍主、乾闥婆乾闥婆主、緊曩羅緊曩羅主，乃至所有惡心者極惡心者，乃至善者極善者，如是等眾皆來集會。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時世尊觀察是會諸大眾已，入毘盧遮那一切金剛曼拏羅莊嚴三摩地已，即於眉間、心間、臍中放大光明照一切世界。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼光明照一切世界已，還復來入金剛相應之心。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時金剛手菩薩，於大眾中整衣肅容從坐而起，手擲金剛詣於佛所，稽首佛足重伸敬禮，禮已合掌而說讚言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今歸命毘盧遮那最上無畏，能說灌頂大陀羅尼成就調伏，欲令有情覺悟不生不滅無相之智，能破輪迴生死大怖。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是讚己重白佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大悲世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b23_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今有疑欲當請問，願賜哀愍而為解說。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金剛阿闍梨作曼拏羅，云何擇地？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "地有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何作淨？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何作橛？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何能破諸惡障難？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何解除諸相禁縛？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至諸龍云何降伏？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又持誦作法云何護摩？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至火法當云何作？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又一切曼拏羅當有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當開幾門？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "門有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其相云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復外曼拏羅當有何義？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "內曼拏羅復有何義？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "中間輪相其義云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼拏羅界云何擘畫？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何絣線？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所作本尊及彼賢聖身量云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "樓閣寶座當高幾許？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至於印契其相云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又粉曼拏羅當云何作？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "粉有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "下粉次第何是先後？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又阿闍梨攝受弟子法則云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "弟子修行先修何法？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又持誦之人所修先行法則云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復弟子入曼拏羅次第云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所奉本尊諸有明契云何傳受？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "獻食出生儀有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於阿闍梨奉獻何物？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復奉獻諸佛如來賢瓶大小之量當有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "瓶項、瓶口當云何作？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復云何作灌頂法？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨法當何所用？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又云何名祕密曼拏羅？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今一一請問如是之事，為欲利樂一切有情，唯願慈悲廣為開說？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說是語已還復本座。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時世尊告金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝金剛手得大無畏具大悲愍，而於我前能發是問，宜應諦聽當為汝說。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時金剛手瞻仰專注受教而住。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "地種廣大各各有相，大略言之而有四種，隨其四姓而分別之。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四姓者，所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "剎帝利、婆羅門、毘舍、首陀。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此者為四。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「擇地之法，隨其香、味或以顏色亦有四種：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一、剎帝利姓求赤色地；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二、婆羅門姓求白色地；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三、毘舍求深黃地；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第四、首陀求黑色地。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又以香氣而擇其地：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "剎帝利地雜蓮花香；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆羅門地青蓮花香；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍之地女觸之香；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "首陀之地雌黃之香。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又以其味而分別之：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "剎帝利地其味如鐵復有甘味；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆羅門地其味辛辣；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0542c29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍之地其味唯甜；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "首陀之地其味苦辣。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是之地當一心專注分別揀擇。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「得是地已，結界釘橛。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作橛之法隨曼拏羅儀亦有四種：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為息災，用有乳木為橛；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為增益，用吉祥木及室利沙木為橛；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為降伏，用佉儞囉木為橛；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為調伏，用鐵為橛。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復若隨祖那忿怒明王真言，用息災法橛；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若用蓮花最上明王真言，當用增益法橛；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若隨大力明王真言，用降伏及調伏法橛。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復若為辟除一切惡及驚怖障難者，當用普光印及槌印及彼真言；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為禁縛極惡之者，當用金剛羯磨及金剛鎖印真言等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此印及真言，若不為極惡不得輒用；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於極惡者用此法後須却解放；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若解放後仍須與彼出生食祭之。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復若於三種火壇作法時、或弟子作先行法時、或作曼拏羅護摩時，所有禁縛調伏諸障難者，以增益一切成就明真言及以香花等，為彼出生用作祭祀。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作曼拏羅者有四種門。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所為東、南、西、北，此為四種。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「其門入者得何果報？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼拏羅有外、有內及與中間，作曼拏羅者作九分量，此九分者是最上曼拏羅。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正擘四門，於此四門所作所求果報各異。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為求大地主、求劍成就、求入修羅宮，乃至安樂及解脫智者，可於東門持誦作法；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為求聖藥成就及豐富財穀，乃至安樂吉祥、息諸災沴者，可於南門持誦作法；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為求一切人愛重、子孫隆盛、財穀豐富、息災安樂者，可於西門持誦作法；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為降伏怨家，及調伏一切極惡之者，或作勇猛之事、擁護持誦之人，可於北門持誦作法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若依真言儀軌修相應行，隨所信樂，於各各門入悉能成就。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若復信樂修相應儀軌，一向專注究於文義求無我法者，入於東門。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次金剛手白世尊言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「外曼拏羅當云何名？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "外曼拏羅名，如彼大寺中有殿塔，必有垣牆以為外護，外曼拏羅亦復如是。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如智果當勤擁護方可得成，外曼拏羅亦復如是；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如子實包在瓤殼，瓤殼在外、子實在內，內曼拏羅亦復如是。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於中心當安子輪，輪相所表顯真實義，或安『迦』字表羯磨義；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『囉』字表智義。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又金剛手白佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b16_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "內外已說，云何是中？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以曼拏羅正分三分，一分是外、一分是內、一分是中。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」金剛手白言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「作曼拏羅絣線云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「作上、中、下絣之。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先以智慧智方便相應三昧，觀想自身化為如來。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此觀成已，後以定印等引如如來金剛風虛空，令一切地界有金剛風遍滿；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復觀彼風輪地上，有金剛明王『無』字印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復觀想四寶金剛山上，有『吽』字名遍現最上大金剛寶峯。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543b27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其上有大寶殿，以金剛寶柱、寶鈴、寶衣、幢幡、瓔珞種種莊嚴，而彼殿中有蓮花寶色如來於中而住，此名三昧曼拏羅。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是觀想一一了知已，復自在行四金剛步，結大惡忿怒明王印及誦真言，作金剛拳無畏行步如舞。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作如是觀察，然後用印真言莊嚴曼拏羅，中間安相獻香花等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有行人，能如是發心一一不失者，乃是行如來真言之教者，當以我威力灌頂法而與灌頂。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼行人如為一切有情三時迴向無上智智果者，應作相應相，思惟一切有情本尊，應當如是一一了知。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又金剛阿闍梨及修行同行乃至弟子，亦須如是解了，然後加持地結界作金剛地。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復以吉祥妙音讚歎訖，先於西北方志心以金剛最上明而為供養；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次於東北方用金剛仗而為供養；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次於東南方用金剛火而為供養；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次於西南方用金剛劍而作供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是供養已，然後阿闍梨將弟子令執線相隨，自西北方擘畫量度，次東北方、次東南方、次西南方。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是擘畫量度定已，然後復自西北起首，順行絣線作界道，作四方相，分三重作內、外、中。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是定已，請金剛阿闍梨作種種供養，於西北方持誦人左邊先結龜印安於地上。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然阿闍梨自西北方起首，右膝著地右手下粉。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先下白粉、次赤粉、次黃粉、次綠粉、最後黑粉。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此下粉次第恒以為式，下粉不得蓋著界道，所下粉亦不得麁細不勻或復曲戾，所下粉先有缺處更添補令全。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又金剛手白世尊言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「用粉五色當何所表？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有何義？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「譬如白色故舊之衣，欲染愛樂之色，必先以水洗濯令淨；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0543c29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既洗淨已白色純粹，然後染成所愛樂色。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令持誦人及與弟子，先有惡業之垢，當以曼拏羅法水洗淨，後用深智義色染成所愛樂色。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其白、赤、黃、綠四色之粉，能滅所犯大梵行罪。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "黑者表摩摩枳菩薩之義，其內曼拏羅中心，當以純白一色畫輪相；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其外曼拏羅所有門及四角，當安置閼伽瓶，其瓶中當滿盛五寶、五藥、五穀等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「閼伽之瓶為有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其量云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "閼伽之瓶當有七種，所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金瓶、銀瓶、銅瓶、玻瓈瓶、鐵瓶、木瓶、瓦瓶。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等瓶是為七種。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為息災、增益及灌頂法，可用金瓶、玻瓈瓶、瓦瓶；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為降伏調伏及作阿修羅法，可用銅瓶；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若作諸忿怒法，可用銀、鐵及木等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼閼伽瓶高二十指，腹闊十六指，項高五指，口廣八指，此等之量為最上。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼拏羅用其瓶色；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為息災法用白色瓶；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若增益法用黃色瓶；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若敬愛法用赤色瓶；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若降伏法用極黑色瓶。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有繫瓶繒帛一隨瓶色。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又降伏法瓶，其項𦟛細乃是吉祥。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」金剛手復白佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何為弟子作灌頂法？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "灌頂曼拏羅其量云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先於大曼拏羅西北方，如內曼拏羅大小量，畫灌頂曼拏羅，中間畫界或三重或七重，四面畫門，於門中各畫本方天王，乃至四隅、上下亦畫本位天王，如天降下勢，各各執持天花、妙鬘等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又用四閼伽瓶，其瓶先以真言一一加持訖，安於四角。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544a28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然於曼拏羅中心畫師子座，畫畢便以多乳木所出之香，及種種花乃至上妙食等而為供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於此曼拏羅所受灌頂者，今生所有一切輕重之罪悉得消滅。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「曼拏羅中諸賢聖身量及色云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至其座高低云何？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼拏羅賢聖而有四種，所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "幖幟、或鑄、或畫、或復木彫。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其量大小應曼拏羅門，隨彼所造當令圓滿，法印具足圓光嚴飾，所造本尊倍令殊勝。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於東方安阿閦佛，身淺青色；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "南方安寶生佛，身淺黃色；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西方安無量壽佛，身純紅色；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "北方安不空成就佛，身大綠寶色。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸如來各各坐於隨方寶座，至於頭冠髮髻種種莊嚴，如諸如來無不具足。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於中方作三界道，以純白色而作心輪，輪中畫毘盧印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又阿閦如來作觸地印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶生如來作施願印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無量壽如來作定印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不空成就如來作施無畏印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "印與真言同用。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又樓閣賢聖於金剛曼拏羅外，別安曼拏羅，廣闊十尺莊嚴具足。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢聖座與佛座稍卑，安排本族賢聖，又本族母、又護世及諸天主等座，高低如曼拏羅；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又夜摩天王及彼天賢聖座高四指。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是作曼拏羅已，其阿闍梨當須志心奉獻花鬘、瓔珞及金剛鈴拂，乃至妙香閼伽等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其閼伽瓶當正造八所或十六所，並須依法滿盛香水。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又用好酥然燈，斯為最上。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或為成就法者，當以白芥子油然燈；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為中下事者，可用常油燃燈。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以花供養者，隨各各法而有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至塗香、燒香等物，吉與不吉而有幾種？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼摩里迦花、無憂花、摩俱羅花、惹帝花、瞻波迦花、喻體迦花、軍那花、儞摩里迦花、怛誐囉花、迦俱婆花，如是諸花皆是吉祥，可遍於三族而用供養；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又瞻波迦花、無憂花、奔曩誐花，如是等花可供養最上曼拏羅；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又俱吒惹花、悉致迦花、黃金花、尸里舍花、建尼迦囉花、俱母那花、優鉢羅花，如是諸花常供養大蓮花族；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又優鉢羅花、怛誐羅花、曲花、迦難𤚥花、波吒羅花、白蓮花，及種種蓮花、妙香花、妙解脫花、調伏花、新末里迦花，如是等花可用供養祕密曼拏羅。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上諸花並是吉祥花，可依法供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又阿俱羅花、迦囉尾囉花，此等花者佛不許用，非吉祥故；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有諸花若是不臭兼及無刺，亦未有人毀折者，可隨力隨分而作供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此為中等，可供養陀羅尼曼拏羅、忿怒曼拏羅。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復有諸香等，於供養義亦有分別。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "白檀、麝香、覩魯瑟迦香、乳香、烏尸覽香、室哩吠瑟吒迦香、𤚥尸香、母瑟吒香、吉薩囉香。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是諸香搗篩為粖，用沙糖和是為和香，此香可用供養最上曼拏羅；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又白檀香、龍腦香、沈香、麝香，及不蚛恭俱摩香，如是等香可用供養中等曼拏羅；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復以安息香、牛角、駝毛，及鼠狼皮等為屑，用摩儞木汁和合為香，如是等香可為調伏法用；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復赤檀香及黑藥、黑毛及苦辣香，如是諸香可於調伏曼拏羅用。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若是隨力隨分得諸妙香者，可用供養陀羅尼曼拏羅、最上忿怒曼拏羅等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0544c29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復以種種飲食奉獻曼拏羅賢聖等，所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥乳、密酪及諸漿飲，及餅、糖餅、油餅、糖食、乳粥，及以種種蔬菜等而為奉獻。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復獻食當用諸器，所謂：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金器、銀器、銅器、瓦器，或以樹葉、或以荷葉、或鉢羅樹葉。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上諸器及葉，但以未觸為最清淨是為最上。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復作息災、增益曼拏羅出生供養，及阿闍梨自食者，但只三白而為最上。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三白者：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乳酪、粳米、飯等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或別三白色食亦得；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或為獻中等曼拏羅諸賢聖即加甜味，食器用銅及葉；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為調伏等事曼拏羅，復加苦辣之味。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其阿闍梨所食不越三白。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復諸曼拏羅，一一皆須外有幢幡、瓔珞、妙香、花鬘、塗香、燒香、燈燭、閼伽水等而為供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a14_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復阿闍梨者，於如上諸曼拏羅相應諸儀則法一一了知，而於本尊真言印契甚深義理而能解了，又復被精進甲冑、執猛利器仗、乘不退車堅修三密，於三界中有大威力，受於人天最上供養。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是阿闍梨常修等引，為諸弟子或作灌頂或作護摩，起曼拏羅而作利益。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復次金剛手言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「凡息災、增益等作護摩事，云何造爐？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何印契？",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸護摩爐，若廣說者有五百種，今隨法說者略有四種：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一息災爐、二增益爐、三敬愛爐、四降伏爐。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至諸成就法及調伏法，亦不離此四種之法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一息災爐者，其狀圓如蓮華相；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二增益爐者，其狀四方縱廣正等；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三三角；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第四如半月。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言印契各各隨法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "息災爐者，其色白，爐緣如蓮花相；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "增益爐者，其色如黃金，作金剛緣；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "降伏爐者，赤黑色及如火焰色；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "敬愛爐者，如半月唯赤色。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸護摩爐隨爐各有印契。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "息災、增益用蓮花印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "敬愛用鉤印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "調伏用根本印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上諸印隨安護摩爐中，其護摩爐高一肘、深十二指，下廣拳指一肘，中心起一小臺，縱廣八指、高二指，上面安印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "息災、增益法，火天位臺高四指、縱廣十二指，中心作蓮花相高二指，於此蓮花上坐火天，其火天身色如乳色，髮髻具足頭冠莊嚴，二手結定印著白衣，眼中出光及『入嚩羅』字來入火中蓮花上坐，光焰熾盛有百千重。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次金剛手！",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作先行法護摩爐，以五色粉塗飾作爐，及以五蓮花而為莊嚴。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其爐外四面周迴安各方本尊印或忿怒明王真言等。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大忿怒明王真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　努瑟吒二合　嚩日囉二合　骨嚕二合馱　賀曩賀曩　吽　㗶吒「大忿怒印：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以左手按心，舒三指，以大指捻小指，右手亦如是，於心前相交如金剛杵。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此印作先行法為最上法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或用發遣一切禁縛，以前右手作印，與入嚩羅真言同用。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「入縛羅真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　入嚩二合羅　吽　㗶吒「復次持誦行人作羯磨火請召火天，可用菩提木、烏曇鉢木、尼俱陀木、多乳樹木為柴，當令濕潤不得乾枯，用燒火作請召法。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「召火天印：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以右手平仰，屈大指入掌中，屈頭指第二節成印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「召火天真言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　阿誐曩二合曳引　𪾼呬曳二合引呬　扇引帝孕二合彌　俱嚕　護多引舍曩引野　娑嚩二合引賀「以此印及真言，請召火天入前火中蓮花中。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持誦人觀想火天，身如雪色，右手持數珠，左手持淨瓶，作慈悲相，面有三目，頭戴寶冠髮髻莊嚴種種具足。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若是他族作曼拏羅用者一切成就，當用各各本族心真言安蓮花中，於後邊蓮花中安白象最上明王印；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "右邊蓮花中安金剛槌；",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "左邊安蓮花，其色如乳汁，於一切處護摩同用，更以閼伽水及香花等奉獻火天。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛母酥尼儀則：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿闍梨手執護摩杓，滿杓作護摩。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「護摩真言：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　吽　誐哩二合恨拏二合　誐哩二合恨拏二合　護多引娑曩引野　悉地孕二合彌　鉢囉二合野蹉　娑嚩二合引賀「金剛母酥尼執杓印：",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以右手執杓，頭指作拳按於爐上，又以二手作寶縛，二小指相交，其餘指如羯磨金剛杵印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "成作此印誦前真言，滿杓作護摩供養火天已，發遣移本位在爐內一邊。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0545c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次作護摩，隨所作法念本尊名號為先法，然後志心供養，依法以滿杓三獻作護摩，復獻金剛槌等真言及印。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0546a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是作已，然後以本所為事，或為息災或為增益，起曼拏羅作種種法，供養賢聖。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0546a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得滿願已，然後發遣請諸賢聖各還本位。",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0546a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」一切如來大祕密王未曾有最上微妙大曼拏羅經卷第一",
        "from": "T18n0889_001:0546a06_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]